h input] Budget: [Tier selection] Timeline: [Your management] 🔍 RESEARCH CONSOLIDATION Competitors: [Your analysis links] Mobbin Patterns: [UI research URLs] Industry Data: [Market research] Client References: [Inspiration links] 🎨 BRAND DIRECTION Style: [Your creative direction] Colors: [Brand guidelines] References: [Design inspiration] ⚙️ AUTOMATION STATUS Workflow: [Ready/In Progress/Complete] Priority: [Your management] Notes: [Special instructions] 🚀 IMMEDIATE ADVANTAGES: AS PROJECT MANAGER, YOU GET: ✅ Complete Edit Control - Change anything, anytime ✅ Research Integration - All links and data in one place ✅ Real-Time Updates - Instant workflow adjustments ✅ Version Tracking - See every change made ✅ Mobile Management - Update from anywhere ✅ Team Collaboration - Multiple people can contribute ✅ Client Transparency - Shared access for client input ✅ Automation Triggering - Updates automatically start workflows OPERATIONAL BENEFITS: ✅ Single Source of Truth - Everything in one document ✅ No Data Loss - Google's automatic saving and backup ✅ Flexible Structure - Add sections as needed ✅ Easy Sharing - Simple link sharing with permissions ✅ Integration Ready - API access for automation 📊 COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE: INDUSTRY STANDARD: Static forms, manual processes, disconnected research YOUR SYSTEM: Dynamic documents, automated workflows, integrated research hub RESULT: 3x faster project management with 5x better organization and 10x more flexibility 🎯 NEXT STEP: Would you like me to create the actual Google Doc template for you to copy and use immediately? I can also set up the Make.com integration blueprint showing exactly how to connect the document changes to your automation workflows. 📄 Download Complete Integration Guide This Google Docs approach gives you the perfect balance of manual control and automation efficiency - you can edit and research in real-time while the system automatically handles the workflow routing based on your updates! do th e next step and