emPages Integration Phase 8: Product Configuration Phase 9: Payment & Shipping Phase 10: E-commerce QA **6. AUTOMATION BLUEPRINTS** - Dart.ai project management setup - Make.com workflow configurations - API integration guides - Webhook setup procedures - Error handling and testing **7. TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS** - Mobbin API integration - EasySite.ai configuration - Google Docs API setup - GemPages template generation - Shopify Liquid integration **8. IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLISTS** - Day 1: Google Docs template deployment - Days 2-3: Make.com automation setup - Days 4-5: Conditional logic testing - Week 2: Pilot project launches - Ongoing: Optimization procedures **9. REVENUE & ROI ANALYSIS** - Pricing tiers by project type - Time vs. revenue optimization - Scalability projections - Cost structure analysis - Profit margin calculations **10. QUALITY CONTROL & BENCHMARKS** - Performance targets (>5% conversion, <3s load time, >95 mobile score) - Brand consistency standards - Client satisfaction metrics - Testing procedures - Revision protocols **DESIGN REQUIREMENTS:** - Modern, clean interface with dark/light mode toggle - Collapsible sections with smooth animations - Sticky navigation sidebar - Copy-to-clipboard buttons for code snippets - Download buttons for templates - Breadcrumb navigation - Quick search functionality - Visual workflow diagrams embedded - Color-coded sections by category - Responsive design for mobile access - Print-friendly styles **COLOR SCHEME:** - Primary: #2563eb (blue) - Success: #10b981 (green) - Warning: #f59e0b (orange) - Info: #8b5cf6 (purple) - Background: #f8fafc (light) / #1e293b (dark) **INTERACTIVE ELEMENTS:** - Expandable/collapsible sections - Tabbed content for related documents - Tooltips for technical terms - Progress indicators for implementation phases - Checklist with checkboxes - Copy buttons for templates and code Include embedded workflow images: - Smart Project Flow: https://mdn.alipayobjects.com/one_clip/afts/img/DHc-QIM