and Generation - Module: OpenAI - Create Completion - Prompt engineering for brand assets - Response parsing and storage Scenario 5: EasySite.ai Website Build - Module: HTTP Request to EasySite.ai API - Content injection from brand assets - Website generation trigger Scenario 6: Conditional E-commerce Extension - Module: Router - E-commerce check - Shopify API integration - GemPages template application Scenario 7: Unified Delivery Package - Module: Google Drive - Create Folder - File aggregation and organization - Client notification email **SECTION 3: GOOGLE CLOUD SETUP** Step-by-step instructions for: - Creating Google Cloud project - Enabling Google Docs API - Creating service account - Generating API credentials - Configuring OAuth consent screen - Setting up webhook URLs **SECTION 4: DART.AI INTEGRATION** Complete setup including: - API key generation - Webhook configuration - Project template creation for each type - Task automation rules - Status update triggers **SECTION 5: VARIABLE MAPPING** Detailed mapping between: - Google Docs fields → Make.com variables - Make.com variables → Dart.ai tasks - Dart.ai outputs → EasySite.ai inputs - All system outputs → Delivery package **SECTION 6: ERROR HANDLING & TESTING** - Common errors and solutions - Testing checklist for each integration point - Debugging procedures - Fallback workflows **SECTION 7: CODE SNIPPETS** Provide actual code for: - Make.com HTTP module configurations (JSON) - Google Apps Script for document parsing - Webhook payload examples - API request examples for all platforms Make it ultra-detailed with copy-paste ready code blocks, actual JSON configurations, and click-by-click setup instructions. Include expected input/output for every step. Excellent! Now let me save this as a URL and create one final comprehensive dashboard document: Using Tool | Save document as url Perfect! Now let me create a final master dashboard that links everything together: Using Tool | Doc View Viewing document Now l